data.description: NEW LISTING ON THE QUIETEST STREET IN POLO! This 3 Bed 1.5 Bath is perfect for you and your family! The oversized yard will fit that giant swing set for the kids or perfect for the dogs to run! The fully insulated garage is the ideal spot to hangout even during these cold winter moments! The property also has some unique features including the custom concrete countertops and the walkout porch off the master bedroom! All of this on the only culd-a-sac in Polo so you don't have to worry about cars driving up and down your road at all hours! Call now to schedule you private showing!
